ida zamonaviy bilimlar hamda taʼlim tizimida ilmiy-amaliy ish tajribasiga ega yuqori malakali mutaxassislarni jalb etish.</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">1. Sport akademiyasining boʻlimlari, fakultetlari va kafedralarini shakllantirish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2. Jismoniy tarbiya va sport sohasida zamonaviy bilimlargahamda <span style="BACKGROUND: white">taʼlim tizimida </span>ilmiy-amaliy ish tajribasiga ega yuqori malakali mahalliy<br />va xorijiy mutaxassislar bilan toʻldirish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">3. Mutaxassislarning professional koʻnikmalari va bilim darajalarini uzluksiz oshirish uchun shart-sharoitlar yaratish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">4. Sifatli taʼlim berishda yuqori malakaga, tajribaga ega boʻlgan professor-oʻqituvchilarni moddiy hamda maʼnaviy ragʻbatlantirish mexanizmini ishlab chiqish va amaliyotga tatbiq etish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">—</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2025/2026 oʻquv yiliga qadar</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span 