E: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">(<i>Sh. Shermatov</i>),</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">5.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasining xususiyatidan kelib chiqib, shtatlar jadvalini ishlab chiqish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasining boshqaruv, pedagog, texnik, xizmat koʻrsatuvchi<br />va oʻquv-yordamchi xodimlari hamda trenerlar tarkibining shtat jadvalini ishlab chiqish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">—</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2025/2026 oʻquv yiliga qadar</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Kambagʻallikni qisqartirish va bandlik vazirligi<br />(<i>B. Musayev</i>),<br />Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan="6" style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 100%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">II. Oʻquv-uslubiy jarayonni takomillashtirish, taʼlim sifati va ilmiy tadqiqotlar samaradorligini oshirish hamda yangi oʻqitish uslublarini joriy etish</span></b></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">6.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasidagi taʼlim yoʻnalishlari<br />va mutaxassisliklari boʻyicha malaka talablari, oʻquv rejalari va fan dasturlarini belgilangan talablar boʻyicha ishlab chiqish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">1. Oʻquv-meʼyoriy hujjatlarni oʻrganish va tahlil qilish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2. Oʻrganish va tahlil natijalari asosida taʼlim yoʻnalishlari<br />va mutaxassisliklari boʻyicha malaka talablari, oʻquv rejalari va fan dasturlarini ishlab chiqish hamda belgilangan tartibda tasdiqlash.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">—</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2025-yil</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">may</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>),</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Oliy taʼlim, fan<br />va innovatsiyalar vazirligi</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">(<i>K. Sharipov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">7.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Taʼlim yoʻnalishlari<br />va mutaxassisliklari uchun darslik va oʻquv qoʻllanmalarini yaratish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Taʼlim yoʻnalishlari<br />va mutaxassisliklari xususiyatini hisobga olgan holda xorijiy tajribalarni oʻrganish orqali yangi darslik va oʻquv qoʻllanmalarini yaratish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Davlat budjeti mablagʻlari</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2024/2025 oʻquv yili davomida</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">8.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Axborot-kutubxona markazini mahalliy hamda xorijiy oʻquv, ilmiy<br />va badiiy adabiyotlar, darsliklar hamda oʻquv qoʻllanmalari bilan toʻldirish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">1. Axborot-kutubxona markazini tashkil qilish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2. Axborot-kutubxona markazini oʻquv-metodik adabiyotlar, axborot materiallari (shu jumladan ularning elektron shakllari), maxsus davriy nashrlar bilan taʼminlash.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">3. Axborot-kutubxona markazi moddiy-texnik bazasini mustahkamlash (mebel, zarur inventar, axborot-kommunikatsiya vositalari).</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Davlat budjeti mablagʻlari</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2026-yil</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">dekabr</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>),<br />Oliy taʼlim, fan<br />va innovatsiyalar vazirligi</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">(<i>K. Sharipov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">9.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasiga xorijiy talabalarni jalb etish choralarini koʻrish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">1. Xorijiy mamlakatlar mehnat bozoridagi talabni oʻrganish va xalqaro taʼlim koʻrgazmalarida ishtirok etish rejasini ishlab chiqish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2. Xorijiy talabalarni jalb etish boʻyicha Oʻzbekiston Respublikasining xorijiy davlatlardagi diplomatik vakolatxonalari bilan aloqalarni oʻrnatish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">3. Xorijiy fuqarolarni toʻlov-kontrakt asosida, shu jumladan, masofaviy taʼlim shaklida oʻqishga qabul qilish va oʻqitishni tashkil etish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasining <span style="COLOR: black">budjetdan tashqari mablagʻlari</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2026/2027 oʻquv yili davomida</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Tashqi ishlar vazirligi<br />(<i>B. Saidov</i>),</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Oliy taʼlim, fan<br />va innovatsiyalar vazirligi<br />(<i>K. Sharipov</i>),</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">10.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasi talabalari uchun maxsus stipendiya joriy qilish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">1. Sport akademiyada tahsil olayotgan talabalarga yilda bir marotaba beriladigan “Yil sportchisi” stipendiyasini taʼsis etish.</span></span></span></span></p><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2. “Yil sportchisi” stipendiyasi nizomini ishlab chiqish va tasdiqlash.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasining <span style="COLOR: black">budjetdan tashqari mablagʻlari</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2026/2027 oʻquv yili davomida</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">11.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-B