n jihozlash.</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="BACKGROUND: white"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif"><span style="COLOR: black">Ilm-fanni moliyalashtirish va innovatsiyalarni qoʻllab-quvvatlash jamgʻarmasi mablagʻlari</span></span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 12%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="BACKGROUND: white"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">2025/2026 oʻquv yiliga qadar</span></span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Innovatsion rivojlanish agentligi<br />(<i>Sh. Rajabbayev</i>),</span></span></span></span></p><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport vazirligi<br />(<i>A. Ikramov</i>)</span></span></span></span></p></td></tr><tr><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: black 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 3%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p align="center" style="TEXT-ALIGN: center"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">14.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 21%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Sport akademiyasining talabalaridan volontyorlik guruhlarini shakllantirish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 27%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: black 1px solid; PADDING-TOP: 0cm" valign="top"><p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; TEXT-INDENT: 11.35pt"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman',serif">Volontyorlik guruhlariga taʼlim yoʻnalishlari boʻyicha iqtidorli talabalar orasidan yetakchilarni saralab olish.</span></span></span></span></p></td><td style="BORDER-BOTTOM: black 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0cm; BACKGROUND-COLOR: white; PADDING-LEFT: 4px; WIDTH: 14%; PADDING-RIGHT: 4px; BORDER-TOP: m